A. The border-color

border-top-color
border-bottom-color
border-left-color
border-right-color

B. The border-style:

none, solid, dotted, dashed, double, groove, ridge, inset, outset, hidden

C. The border-width

inherent, thin, thick, medium, can also select in pixels example border-width: 10px

The code is below:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>CSS Border Styles Application</title>
        <style type="text/css">
            h3.header { border: 3px solid; text-align: center; }
            div.section {
                border: 3px solid;
                border-top-color: #ff00ff;
                border-bottom-color: #990000;
                border-left-color: #0000ff;
                border-right-color: #229944;
                border-style:groove;
                border-width: 10px; 
            }
        
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h3 class="header">CSS Border Styles Application</h3>
        <div class="section">
        <p>Hey YouTubers!</p>
        <p>Welcome to Software Developer Tube Channel</p>
        <p>I provide free Programming Tutorials</p>
        </div>
    </body>

</html>
